---
title: Southeast Asian Pork Stir-fry with Thai Sweet Chilli Veggies & Garlic Rice
description: Whip up a tasty bowl of quick-cooking pork strips tossed with colourful veggies and an easy sauce packed with umami flavours. It’s a takeaway standard made at home in a flash!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southeast-asian-pork-stir-fry-9b60c2f7.jpg
